I hit a situation where `PrefixModules` should be duplicating modules, but it is not.

Consider the following:

```
circuit Top : %[[
  {
    "class":"sifive.enterprise.firrtl.NestedPrefixModulesAnnotation",
    "target":"~Top|Foo",
    "prefix":"A_",
